-- Ukraine Seizes $7.5 Million of Cocaine Hidden in Pineapples
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2012-02-06T15:07:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-06/ukraine-seizes-7-5-million-of-cocaine-hidden-in-pineapples.html
Ukraine seized more than 38 kilograms
(84 pounds) of cocaine hidden in pineapples shipped from  Costa
Rica , with law-enforcement agencies valuing the drugs at more
than $7.5 million.  The customs service, the State Security Service and border
guards confiscated the shipment from a container in the port of
Illichivsk, the security service in the capital, Kiev, said
today in a  statement  on its website.  Five people were arrested on Feb. 4-6, according to the
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 dkrasnolutsk@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
